Variable.Name: ShowErr

Variable.Name: PgLimit
Variable.Comment: Pages limit. 2 = IPv6 disabled / 4 = IPv6 enabled

Variable.Name: DisableIP_msk
Variable.Comment: Time shown in the UI to set the countdown after which the EnIPCFG is set to false

Variable.Name: IntervalReadIP_msk
Variable.Comment: Time interval shown in the UI, between each IP reading

Variable.Name: DisableConstantReading
Variable.Comment: Enable shown in the UI to turn on/off the continuous IP reading

Variable.Comment: Previous IntervalReadIP_msk - It changes once the variable has changed

Variable.Name: PrevDisableIP_msk
Variable.Comment: Previous DisableIP_msk - It changes once the variable has changed

Variable.Name: ErrorSignalCnt
Variable.Comment: Used to reboot the c.pCO only if there was no error

Variable.Comment: If true resets the (default) 20 min timer. It's used to know it the user is still in the mask
